    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major restoration project or a source for spare parts. The body has significant rust issues, particularly on the undercarriage and wheel arches, and the paint is heavily faded with several deep scratches. Mechanically, the car requires substantial work to be roadworthy again, as the engine runs roughly and the transmission shows signs of slipping. The interior is also heavily worn, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics.",
