    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This impeccably maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical upkeep and a refined interior, it offers a balanced synthesis of performance and longevity. Thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for operational excellence, this motorcar is prepared for immediate delivery. Experience a vehicle that balances sophisticated engineering with enduring value.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion on the road. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs smoothly, and the interior still feels super cozy and well-kept. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s definitely ready to hit the road for its next chapter with you! It\u2019s a fantastic ride that won\u2019t let you down. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this platform is renowned for. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday comfort. This car has been a reliable companion, and its condition reflects a history of careful ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish; while you may find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper typical of highway driving, the body remains straight and free of major blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary featuring well-preserved upholstery and high-quality materials. All electronic components, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. I have adhered to a rigorous maintenance schedule, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the braking system feels firm and responsive. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride with a transmission that shifts seamlessly through every gear. This is an honest, solid vehicle perfect for someone seeking a dependable drive with a touch of luxury. Includes a complete service history and two sets of keys.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the sophisticated buyer. Presenting in commendable condition, the automobile exhibits a refined aesthetic paired with robust mechanical integrity. Every aspect of this vehicle has been curated to ensure a seamless transition to its next owner, offering a balanced synthesis of performance and long-term value. We invite you to inspect this exemplary model and appreciate the standard of excellence it maintains.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great and feels smooth, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This unit is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable differential lock. The mechanicals are sound; the VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the rear subframe has been inspected for stress fractures to ensure structural rigidity. Suspension remains tight with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of this chassis. Minor cosmetic wear is present, but the powertrain and drivetrain syncopation remain sharp for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
